Output dbt-real.gif
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1000
Set Height 560
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 14
Hide
Type "export PATH=/tmp/bftest-dbt/venv/bin:$HOME/.local/bin:$PATH BACKFILL_API=https://backfill.sh DBT_PROFILES_DIR=/tmp/bftest-dbt/proj && cd /tmp/bftest-dbt/proj && clear"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Show
Type "bf dbt run"
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 16s
